<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Glenbrook</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
        <p class="par-lg">Just north of Glamorgan in the South West Calgary, lies the quiet and picturesque neighborhood of Glenbrook. </p>
        <p class="par-lg">Home to an eclectic mix of residential dwellings ranging from single-family detached homes, townhouses to condominiums and low-rise apartments, the community in Glenbrook offers a divine combination of the relaxed appeal of the suburbs and the vibrant life of the city. </p>
        <p class="par-lg">The Glenbrook real estate also offers a plethora of recreational facilities including a swimming pool, an indoor ice skating rink, golf courses and a myriad of shopping complexes to keep your busy and entertained.</p>
        </div>
